# Sales & Products SQL Analysis

## ðŸ“Š Project Overview

This project showcases **intermediate-level SQL querying skills** by analyzing sales and product data stored in a relational database. The queries are designed to answer common **business and reporting questions** such as total sales volume, average pricing by category, daily revenue trends, high-performing products, sales classification, and price-based product segmentation.


